snippet: Police in a Southern California city found an unusual stolen item this week in the back of a compact car with tinted windows - a live, three-day-old calf, an animal welfare official said on Friday....

headline.print_headline: California Man Arrested With Live Calf in the Back of His Car
headline.main: California Man Arrested With Live Calf in the Back of His Car

lead_paragraph: Police in a Southern California city found an unusual stolen item this week in the back of a compact car with tinted windows - a live, three-day-old calf, an animal welfare official said on Friday.
